  "title": "Senior/Design Engineer (Infrastructure works/A1 Main Con/ North or East)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experienced in infrastructure design, focusing on road and viaduct projects.</li>\n  <li>Supervised drafting for project documentation.</li>\n  <li>Prepared designs, sketches, reports, and calculations.</li>\n  <li>Provided drafting staff with details for drawings, material lists, and cost estimates.</li>\n  <li>Assisted in technical details for quotations, contracts, and specifications.</li>\n  <li>Prepared technical submissions for materials, construction methods, and C&amp;S shop drawings.</li>\n  <li>Coordinated with suppliers, clients, consultants, and engineers.</li>\n  <li>Participated in project planning.</li>\n  <li>Experienced in Singapore and international infrastructure design standards.</li>\n  <li>Attended site inspections as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>5 years of design experience in infrastructure works.</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of local design codes and statutory requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p>\n<p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p>\n<p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
